        "human_examples": [
            "Water's finally warm. Kayaks go out at 9, first come first served. No need to call ahead unless you're rolling deep.",
            "Caught the morning calm on Neabsco Creek today. This is the stuff you don't get on a Saturday afternoon.",
            "Pontoon's open this weekend. Bring the cooler, bring the people, we'll handle the rest.",
            "Weekday on the river > weekend on the river. Quieter water, easier launch, and you're not fighting for a parking spot. Just saying.",
            "Featherstone refuge is wide open right now. Herons everywhere. Grab a paddleboard and go see for yourself.",
            "Birthday? Bachelor thing? Just a Tuesday you wanted to make better? Pontoon fits 'em all.",
            "Half the fun is the not-planning. Show up, grab a kayak, figure out the rest on the water.",
