        "caption_patterns": {
            "recreational_boating": "An easy day on the Potomac is closer than you think. Grab a pontoon, gather your crew, and spend the day cruising Neabsco Creek and the river. Plan your day: potomacboatrentals.com",
            "fishing": "Quiet water, good fishing, no boat to own. Launch from Hampton's Landing and work the creeks and shoreline of the Potomac. Weekdays are calmest, so come find your spot.",
            "kayak_sup": "No plans, no reservation, no problem. Our single and double kayaks and paddleboards are first come, first served. Just show up and explore Neabsco Creek. Big group? Give us a call.",
            "weekday_push": "Skip the weekend crowds. Weekdays on the Potomac mean quieter water, easier launches, and the river mostly to yourself. Make a weekday plan.",
            "group_event": "Birthdays, bachelor and bachelorette parties, team outings: a pontoon on the Potomac makes it easy. Gather the group and we'll get you on the water.",
